function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	--Yulia Move + Bark
	cloneYULIA = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_YULIA)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cloneYULIA) then
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_YULIA, id_Self, cloneYULIA)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(cloneYULIA, CONVO_YULIA)
		Hydra.QActorWait(cloneYULIA, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(cloneYULIA, LOC_YULIA, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(cloneYULIA, 1)
	end
		
	--Follower to Static + Bark
	idKrys = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_KRYS_FOLLOWER)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idKrys) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idKrys)
		Hydra.QActorEnableAI(idKrys, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idKrys, ID_KRYS_ARRIVE, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idKrys, ID_KRYS_ARRIVE)
		
		--Follower Bark + Anim
		Hydra.QActorWait(idKrys, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idKrys, ANIM_PRAY)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idKrys, CONVO_YULIA)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idKrys)
		--Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idKrys, "QST_UNFLESH_ARRIVE", idSelf)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_KRYS, id_Self, idKrys)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idKrys, CONVO_KRYS)
				
		Hydra.QActorWait(idKrys, 0.5)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idKrys)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	--Hydra.QActorSheath
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()	

	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_KRYS_CLOSE, 1)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_FEODOR, id_Self, ID_KRYS_CLOSE)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_KRYS_CLOSE,CONVO_FEODOR)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_KRYS_CLOSE, 1)
			
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	--Static Run from A to B
	CloneKrysEnd = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_KRYS_CLOSE)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(CloneKrysEnd, LOC_KRYS_END, "NPC_WALK", true)
	Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(CloneKrysEnd, 1)
	
end

function Start(snoQuest, idActorFollower)
	
	followerKrys = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_KRYS_FOLLOWER)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerKrys) then 
		Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(followerKrys)
	end

end
